list.name: Default
list.comment: Fixed buld issue. If you mark src as sources root, build fails because src/scala is also set as sources root. When this happens, classes are generated twice and nothing builds. Shit ain't smart, yo.

task.summary: Changed project to have a build.sbt file. I'm not sure if I should commit the "target" folder, seems like a cache to me. Needs to be investigated.
